trans-unit.source: A block-level flow content element which enables <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> elements (i.e. a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"></xref>) to be embedded (hosted) in flow content.
trans-unit.target: Ett element med innehåll på blocknivå flödet som gör att <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> element (d.v.s. en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"> </xref>) att bädda in (värd) i flödet innehåll.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> element (i.e. a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>) may be embedded directly in flow content by enclosing it in a BlockUIContainer (see example below).
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>element (d.v.s. en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>) kan vara inbäddat direkt i flödet innehåll inom en BlockUIContainer (se exemplet nedan).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: An BlockUIContainer may directly host no more than one <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> child.
trans-unit.target: En BlockUIContainer kan direkt värd för fler än en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>underordnade.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: However, the child element hosted by an BlockUIContainer may host children of its own.
trans-unit.target: Det underordnade elementet hos en BlockUIContainer kan dock vara värd för sin egen underordnade.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new, empty instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny, tom instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"></xref> class, taking a specified <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> object as the initial contents of the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"> </xref> klass, tar en angiven <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> -objektet som det inledande innehållet i den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> object specifying the initial contents of the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> objekt som anger det inledande innehållet i den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> hosted by the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> som är värd för den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer> may directly host no more than one <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> child.
However, the child element hosted by an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer> may host children of its own.
trans-unit.target: Men det underordnade elementet som är värd för en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer>kan vara värd för sin egen underordnade.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer>

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlexaml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], wrapping a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> in an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer> is equivalent to setting that <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> as the value of the Child property.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlexaml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], wrapping en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>i en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer>ställer som motsvarar <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>som värde för egenskapen underordnade.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockUIContainer> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>
